ction to satisfy your sweet cravings while ensuring a guilt-free treat.\r\nAt Chitale Bandhu Mithaiwale, our legacy dates back to 1950, where we embarked on a journey to deliver authentic Indian sweets that capture the essence of tradition. Our No Added Sugar Kaju Katli is a testament to our commitment to quality and taste.\r\nOur Kaju Katli retains the rich flavor and melt-in-the-mouth goodness that has made it a cherished favorite for generations. The absence of added sugar makes it an excellent choice for those seeking a healthier option without compromising on taste.\r\nYou can savor the freshness of our Kaju Katli for up to 30 days. Store it in a cool, dry place, and indulge at your own pace, knowing that every piece is crafted with care.',999,'2024-01-23T190636.864790_chitale-kaju-katli.jpg',720,'23-01-2024 19:06.36','Kaju Katli (No Added Sugar) from Chitale Bandhu – Pune',9,1);
